race.comment: POLITICAL OATH (2) could only manage eighth two runs back then improved last start but found a couple better over 302m at this track, beaten only 1.5 lengths after being in contention on the corner. Best figures measure up. Sure to run well. BLACK CHILITA (1) finished 0.6 lengths from the winner in fourth last start after being prominent at the bend over 201m at Gillespie County Fairground, an improvement on her first-up sixth at Retama Park the run before. This looks a sterner test than last time but on her best form she is capable of testing her rivals. DASHINGTHEDAYAWAY (8) was in the firing line on the turn and finished second last start over 229m at Retama Park (Dirt), beaten 0.8 lengths. Nicely placed to go one better. HIGH DASHING (9) has filled a minor placing at her last three outings, most recently when third over 274m at this track (Dirt). Suitably placed so anticipating another big run.
